 2020-03962020-05-30,  GAC,  ,  , 
ActUnited Nations Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the United Nations Al-Qaida and Taliban Regulations
PrecisRegulations amending the THE UNITED NATIONS AL-QAIDA AND TALIBAN REGULATIONS in order to (1) fulfill Canada's international legal obligation to implement the binding decisions of the Security Council set out in Resolutions 2253 (2015), 2255 (2015) and 2368 (2017); and (2) address miscellaneous amendments raised by the Standing Joint Committee for the Scrutiny of Regulations.
